  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个TCP报文结构的示意图，用于给风控团队讲解FinTech_AuthVault的传输层封装。重点是让源端口和目的端口在前32位清晰呈现，然后序列号和确认号各占32位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以0-15位是源端口，16-31位是目的端口。那数据偏移和保留字段怎么安排？还有六个标志位需要单独标出来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，数据偏移占4位（96-99），保留6位（100-105）。六个标志位每个1位，按URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN的顺序从106到111。特别要注意的是ACK和URG这两个标志，在身份验证流程里会频繁用到。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，标志位序列确认了。接下来是窗口大小和校验和吧？窗口16位，校验和也是16位？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "Checksum"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，112-127是Window，128-143是Checksum。然后紧急指针16位放在144-159。这里有个特殊需求——我们要在160-191位标注FinTech_AuthVault，这是我们的自定义扩展字段，替代传统的选项字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画到160-191位标注FinTech_AuthVault了。最后192-255是数据载荷部分对吧？整个报文标题用\"TCP Packet Structure\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data",
        "TCP Packet Structure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，确认号拼写需要改一下——应该是Acknowledgment不是Acknowledgement，美式拼写少一个e。另外紧急指针的英文也请确认是Urgent Pointer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "Urgent Pointer"
